{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/241104_kala_VAMPIRESANDWICH_SteamStorePage_GraphicalAssets_description_1.gif?t=1731744644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VAMPIRE SANDWICH</strong> is a roguelike deckbuilder,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">where you craft and stack sandwiches to serve vampire girls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(Press &quot;Request Access&quot; above to join\u00a0<strong>Steam</strong>\u00a0beta Playtest!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UNIQUE SANDWICH-BUILDING MECHANICS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stack, stack, stack over 100 unique ingredient cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover your own creative sandwich synergy and combos!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPERIENCE THE WORLD OF VAMPIRES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience stories with characters that change every day. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hungry vampires may attack you for blood if you don't meet them for too long!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/241109_kala_VAMPIRESANDWICH_SteamStorePage_GraphicalAssets_description_2_150speed_.gif?t=1731744644\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VISUAL NOVEL-STYLE ROGUELIKE DECKBUILDER EXPERIENCE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn rewards for fun dates with vampire beauties and maids. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll get better rewards for making choices that please your characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014370/extras/241104_kala_VAMPIRESANDWICH_SteamStorePage_GraphicalAssets_description_3.gif?t=1731744644\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">    BEWARE THEIR THIRST</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vampires don't settle for tasteless sandwiches!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep making delicious sa